chapters.title: A Method of Teaching that God Uses

And We'Ll Read Verse 8 and 9 It Says and Let Them Make Me a Sanctuary That I May Dwell among Them According to all That I Show Thee after the Pattern of the Tabernacle and the Pattern of All the Instruments Air for Even Shall You Make It You See When Moses Was in Mount Sinai and God Was Giving Him Instruction as to How To Build the Tabernacle He Didn't Give Him a Blueprint He Didn't Give Him a Plan on Paper He Showed Him Our Sanctuary for Him to Pattern the Earthly Sanctuary on this Is all Explained Wonderfully in the Book of Hebrews

We Have Such a High Priests with a Set on the Right Hand of the Throne of the Majesty in the Heaven a Minister of the Sanctuary and of the True Tabernacle Which the Lord Pitched and Not Men Did You Catch What It Just Said Here It Says First that Geez Is a High Priests but He's Not a High Priest in a Earthly Sanctuary He's a High Priest in a Heavenly Sanctuary That God Himself Has Pitched Not Men Verse 3 It Says for every High Priest Is Ordained To Offer Gifts and Sacrifices Wherefore

This Man Have Somewhat Also To Offer So Whatever Was Happening on the Earthly Sanctuary Is a Reflection and Image a Shadow of What Is Happening in the Heavenly Sanctuary and if if the Earthly Priest Would Offer Sacrifice and Jesus Is Dupre See Also Has To Offer a Sacrifice and Here We Read this Exactly for if He Were on Earth that Jesus He Would Not Be a Priest Saying that They Are Priests That Offer Gifts According to the Law So Obviously Jesus Is Not a Priest on Earth because There's Already Priests Here Going on Verse 5 Who Serve on to the Example and Shadow of Heavenly Things as Moses Was Admonished of God When He Was About To Make the Tabernacle for Sea

And More Perfect Tabernacle Not Made with Hands That Is Not of this Building neither by the Blood of Goats and Calves but by His Own Blood He Entered in Once into the Holy Place Having Obtained Eternal Redemption for Us Here We Learn that Indeed Christ Came In with Blood Just as the Priest Would Coming with Blood but He Didn't Come with a Blood of Goats and Bulls because that Can't Make Anyone Perfect the Bible Said so He Came with His Own Blood That Is What Jesus Came into Heaven to Minister with His Own Blood To Make Atonement for My Sins and Your Sins Verse 23 It Was Therefore Necessary that the Patterns of Things in the Heaven Should Be Purified with these but the Heavenly Things Themselves with Better Sacrifices than these so as the Pattern Which Was on Earth Needed To Be Cleansed with Blood

Once at the End this Is Speaking of the High Priest Ministry of the Day of Atonement Priest Would Do It every Year Christ Will Do It Once at the End of the Day He Will Perform the Cleansing of the Sanctuary the Day of Atonement in Heaven Verse 27 and as It Is Appointed unto Men Once To Die but after this the Judgment Here's the Connection so Christ Was Once Offered To Bear the Sins of Many and to Them That Look for Him Shall He Appear the Second Time without Sin unto Salvation So There You Have It at the End of Time There Is Going To Be a Day of Atonement

So Christ Was Once Offered To Bear the Sins of Many and to Them That Look for Him Shall He Appear the Second Time without Sin unto Salvation So There You Have It at the End of Time There Is Going To Be a Day of Atonement the One That Was on Earth Was a Typical It Was a Type but the Day of Atonement in Heaven Is an Anti-Type It's What It Really Is All about the One on Earth Was Only Teaching Us What Would Be Happening in Heaven and Then We Read that after that Would Be the Second Coming Christ Would Come Back this Is a Perfect Match of Actually What Daniel

And Then We Read that after that Would Be the Second Coming Christ Would Come Back this Is a Perfect Match of Actually What Daniel Has Been Seeing the Day of Atonement on Earth Was a Type a Figure of What Crisis High Priests Will Do in Heaven so You Know What We Need To Do Now because We Have a 2300 Day Prophecy that 2300 Day Prophecy See Actually Will Tell Us Exactly When this Day of Atonement in Heaven Will Take Place We Will Know Exactly When the Judgment Will Begin and all We Have To Do Is We Need Two of Three Element the Time Prophecy in each Three Things It Needs a Start a Duration or an N and We Have a Duration Already So if We Can Find the Start We Will Know When the Day of Atonement in Heaven Will Begin

And We Read Let's Go to Verse 26 after He's Talked about the Little Horn It Says a Division of the Evening in the Morning Which Was Told Is True this Is Going To Happen Wherefore Shut Up the Vision for It Shall Be for Many Days Gabriel Just Told Him To Close It Why because It Says that I Daniel Fainted and What Six Certain Days Afterward I Rose Up and Did the King's Business and I Was Astonished at the Vision but None Understood It Daniel Saw the Vision Gabriel Was About To Explain Them but Daniel Overwhelm Fainted and So We Are Missing a Crucial Element To Know When the 2300 Days Will End but Let's Not Despair because the Answer Is Actually in the Following Chapter in Chapter 9 but that Will Be for Next Week for Now Remember God Is Working on Our Behalf in Heaven

But Part of that Preparation Is for You and I To Repent from Our Sins To Gain a Victory over the Sins To Live a Victorious Life like Christ Showed Us We Can Live Right Here and Right Now before the Judgment Closed before Probation Closes and before Our Fate Is Eternally Decided Let's Do the Work That We Need To Do in Order To Not Be Cut Off and Rather Be Counted among the Saints of the Most High Let Us Pray Father I Thank You Lord There's So Much Wealth Is So Much Beauty in the Scripture for Us To Know To Understand Father You Have Not Left That Is in the Dark You Have Prepared

I Thank You Lord There's So Much Wealth Is So Much Beauty in the Scripture for Us To Know To Understand Father You Have Not Left That Is in the Dark You Have Prepared Us You Are Preparing Us so that We Make It We Can Stand in the End Father Thank You for the Ministry of Jesus a Ministry That Began on Earth and that Continues in Heaven Father Thank You for Our High Priest Who Knows the Feeling of Our Infirmities We Can Plead and Minister for Us Who Can Intercessor for Us Our Advocate Father Thank You for Doing Everything in Your Power To Make Sure that We Are Saved and It's for Us Now Father through Your Strain To Do What Is Right
